\v 2 Basebemenzela ukudla kwantambama lapho\x + Mat. 26.6. Mark. 14.3.\x*, loMarta wayesebenza\x + Luka 10.38,39.\x*\x + Luka 10.40.\x*; njalo uLazaro wayengomunye walabo ababehlezi ekudleni laye.
