\v 3 UMariya\x + Luka 10.38,39.\x* wasethatha iphawundi yamagcobo \w awenadi\w** uqobo adulayo\x + 19.39.\x*, wagcoba inyawo zikaJesu\x + Luka 7.38. Mat. 26.7. Mark. 14.3.\x*, wesula inyawo zakhe ngenwele zakhe; lendlu yagcwala iphunga lamagcobo.
\v 4 Ngakho omunye wabafundi bakhe, uJudasi Iskariyothi kaSimoni, owayezamnikela\x + 6.71. Mat. 26.8. Mark. 14.4.\x*, wathi:
\v 5 Kungani amafutha la engathengiswanga \w ngabodenariyo\w** abangamakhulu amathathu, kwasekunikwa abayanga\x + Mark. 14.5.\x*?
\v 6 Wakutsho-ke lokhu, kungeyisikho ukuthi ekhathalele abayanga, kodwa ngoba wayelisela, wayelesikhwama\x + 13.29.\x*, ethwala okwakufakwa \add phakathi kwaso\x + 20.15.\x*\add*.
\v 7 UJesu wasesithi: Myekeleni; uwalondolozele usuku lokungcwatshwa kwami\x + Mat. 26.12.\x*.
\v 8 Ngoba abayanga lihlala lilabo, kodwa mina kalihlali lilami.
