\v 9 Ngakho ixuku elikhulu lamaJuda lakwazi ukuthi ulapho; laselisiza kungesikuthi ngenxa kaJesu kuphela, kodwa lokuthi babone loLazaro\x + 8.22.\x*, ayemvuse kwabafileyo\x + 11.43,44.\x*.
\v 10 Abapristi abakhulu\x + Seb. 5.17. 23.8. Luka 16.31.\x* basebesenza icebo lokuthi babulale loLazaro\x + Seb. 5.33.\x*;
\v 11 ngoba ngenxa yakhe\x + 12.18.\x* amaJuda amanengi\x + 8.30.\x* asuka, akholwa kuJesu\x + 8.22.\x*.
\s UJesu ungena eJerusalema
\p
\v 12 Kusisa ixuku elikhulu\x + Mat. 21.4-9. Mark. 11.7-10. Luka 19.35-38.\x* elalizile emkhosini\x + 11.55.\x*, lezwa ukuthi uJesu uyeza eJerusalema,
\v 13 bathatha ingatsha zezihlahla zelala, baphuma uku\add ya\add*mhlangabeza, bamemeza \add besithi\add*: \w Hosana\w**! Ubusisiwe ozayo ebizweni leNkosi, iNkosi kaIsrayeli\x + Luka 19.38.\x*.
\v 14 UJesu wasefica ithole likababhemi, wahlala phezu kwalo, njengokulotshiweyo \add ukuthi\add*:
