\v 20 Kwakukhona amaGriki phakathi kwalabo\x + Seb. 17.4. Joha. 7.35.\x* ababenyukelele ukukhonza\x + 1 Kho. 8.41,42. Seb. 8.27. Luka 2.4.\x* emkhosini\x + 12.1,12. 11.55.\x*;
