\v 25 Yena othanda impilo yakhe uyalahlekelwa yiyo\x + Mat. 10.39.\x*; lozonda impilo yakhe kulumhlaba uzayilondoloza kuze kube yimpilo engulaphakade\x + Luka 14.26.\x*.
